title: Last of Three Convicted Al Jazeera Journalists Leaves Egypt
text:
DUBAI—The last of three Al Jazeera English journalists who had been imprisoned in Egypt has left the country and arrived in Qatar, where the network is based.
Al Jazeera spokesman Hasan Salim Patel confirmed Baher Mohamed’s arrival in the Qatari capital, Doha, on Wednesday. He said he is in the country for a temporary visit.
